"Create, connect, manage, and monitor how your form submissions are "
"automatically synced to Google Sheets in real time."
msgstr ""
"Crea, conecta, gestiona y monitorea cómo se sincronizan automáticamente tus "
"envíos de formularios con Google Sheets en tiempo real."

